  "response": "There could be several reasons why IFTTT won't link to your Tumblr account:\n\n1. Authentication issues\n- Your Tumblr login credentials might be incorrect\n- You may need to re-authorize the connection\n- Tumblr may have changed its API policies\n\n2. Account problems\n- Your Tumblr account might be suspended or restricted\n- You might not have the latest version of the Tumblr app or service\n- There could be a temporary issue with Tumblr's servers\n\n3. IFTTT-specific problems\n- The Tumblr service might be temporarily unavailable on IFTTT\n- Your IFTTT account might have connection restrictions\n\nRecommended troubleshooting steps:\n- Log out and log back into both Tumblr and IFTTT\n- Check your internet connection\n- Update the IFTTT app/service\n- Verify your Tumblr account is active\n- Try connecting again after some time\n- Contact IFTTT support if the problem persists\n\nWould you like me to suggest more specific troubleshooting steps?",
